name: Family To Type And Back
description:
The nodes in this package allow you to get the family of a given family type/symbol or get all family types/symbols of a given family. Contains the nodes: 
* Get Family Symbols From Family, 
* Get Family From family Type.
contents: Get Family Symbols From Family - Gets all family symbols of a given category in the model  (does *not *work for system families), Get Family From Family Type - Retrieves the family of a given family type
